OL,6,FDisgraced ex-BBC TV presenter Huw
OL,7,FEdwards has resigned from two honorary
OL,8,Fpositions at his former university in
OL,9,FWales.
OL,11,FThere have been calls for the 62-year-
OL,12,Fold former newsreader's various
OL,13,Fhonours and awards to be rescinded
OL,14,Fafter he pleaded guilty in July to
OL,15,Fmaking indecent images of children.
