OL,6,FOn Thursday he was stripped of his
OL,7,Fmembership of the prestigious Gorsedd
OL,8,Fof the Bards Welsh arts association,
OL,9,Fand a number of other bodies have
OL,10,Fconfirmed they are reviewing his
OL,11,Fhonours.
OL,13,FA Cardiff University spokesman
OL,14,Fconfirmed to the PA news agency on
OL,15,FFriday that Edwards resigned from both
OL,16,Fhis honorary professor title in the
OL,17,Fschool of journalism, media and
OL,18,Fculture, and honorary fellowship.
