OL,6,F"He is no longer an honorand of the
OL,7,Funiversity," the spokesman said. "Our
OL,8,Fwebsite listing of honorary fellows
OL,9,Fhas been updated accordingly."
OL,11,FEdwards, who graduated in French from
OL,12,FCardiff University, is also no longer
OL,13,Fan honorary fellow of Swansea
OL,14,FUniversity, the body confirmed.
OL,16,FHis honorary fellowship of the Royal
OL,17,FWelsh College Of Music And Drama has
OL,18,Falso been withdrawn following a
OL,19,Funanimous vote by the college's board
OL,20,Fof trustees, a spokesperson for the
OL,21,Fcollege said.
