OL,6,FA spokesman for York St John
OL,7,FUniversity said: "In light of the
OL,8,Foutcome of legal proceedings on
OL,9,FWednesday July 31 2024, the
OL,10,Funiversity's honorary awards committee
OL,11,Fhas taken the decision to rescind Mr
OL,12,FEdwards' honorary award with immediate
OL,13,Feffect."
OL,15,FEdwards became an honorary doctor of
OL,16,Fletters at the Yorkshire education
OL,17,Finstitution in 2019.
